product.name: RedLemon 75X60 Inches L Shaped Electric Standing Desk, Height Adjustable Corner Gaming Desk with Drawers, Keyboard Tray, Power Outlets & LED Lights, Computer Desk with Monitor Shelf, Antique White
product.description:
Where exquisite design meets unbeatable quality and affordability. Our l shaped standing desk combines beauty and durability for you.
One-touch Height Adjustment with four memory positions
More storage space to separate work and personal tasks
Convenient 2 metal hooks for hanging bags, headphones, and 360° rotatable cup holder for sports bottle
Keep the desk stable, Prevent it from sliding on smooth floors
Enjoy your visual feast-Baby blue(shot on a smartphone)
Enjoy your visual feast-Dark blue(shot on a smartphone)
Enjoy your visual feast-Light green(shot on a smartphone)
Enjoy your visual feast-Pink(shot on a smartphone)
Enjoy your visual feast-Purple(shot on a smartphone)
product.bullet_points:
• Adjustable Desk: This Electric standing desk freely selects adjustable standing desk height ranges from 28" to 46". It has 4 height-memorizing features that allow you to control the height easily by pressing a button.
• LED Light: The home office desk has RGB LED light, and 12 scene modes, which can be switched cyclically. When entertaining, dim the lights and choose your favorite colors to fully immerse yourself in the game. When working, match your favorite color to make you work more focused
• Spacious Workspace: the monitor shelf provides a comfortable height and better control of the distance from your eyes and the angle of the screen. The under-shelf store's office supplies and displays decorative items without compromising your workspace. 60 * 60 inches allows you to use one part as your office area and the other part as your study and entertainment area
• More intimate design: The computer desk has several convenient features. It has built-in power outlets, allowing easy charging of devices such as laptops and smartphones. On both sides of the desk, handy hooks are provided for hanging items, keeping your essentials within reach. The desk also features a 360-degree rotating cup holder, ensuring you can enjoy your beverages without worrying about spills. Additionally, it comes with a keyboard tray, providing a designated space for comfortable typing. Lastly, the desk offers two drawers for storing small items, helping you organize your workspace.
• Excellent After-sales Service： Our clear assembly instructions and labeled parts make putting it together a breeze. The product will be shipped in sturdy boxes surrounded by thick foam and wooden protective panels to provide maximum protection from damage during shipping. If you encounter any issues during assembly, our dedicated support team is here to provide professional assistance and ensure your satisfaction.
